Phobia reaches his ship turns to kluster "It has been a successful 
negotiation, until the end of the week then." He extends his hand to 
Kluster as a gesture of the trust shared between the two.

With the other hand he touched his Predacon symbol, the ramp slid 
open awaiting his boarding.
